# .cursorrules —  Wealth & Card Tracking System

> This file is the single source of truth for all AI-assisted development.
> Read it fully before generating any code. When in doubt, re-read it.

---

## 1. Project Overview

A **privacy-first**, single-user personal finance dashboard for tracking:
- Multi-currency bank accounts and credit card balances
- Investment holdings (stocks, crypto) with real-time market value
- Credit card reward points / cashback with a dynamic rule engine
- Net worth across all asset and liability accounts

**Core design principle**: Two tables (`accounts` + `transactions`) model every
financial entity and every money/points movement in the system.

---

## 2. Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 14 (App Router) |
| Language | TypeScript — strict mode, no `any` |
| Database / Auth | Supabase (PostgreSQL) |
| UI Components | shadcn/ui |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS only |
| State Management | React Server Components + Server Actions (primary) · `zustand` (complex client state only) |
| Charts | `recharts` (shadcn-compatible) |
| Decimal Math | `Decimal.js` |
| Auth Package | `@supabase/ssr` **only** |

---

